 Create a .gitignore at the repo root (/home/matt/voyage-35-video-mm/.gitignore) with:
                   
    # Downloaded videos and processed segments
    backend/videos/                            
        
    # Environment variables (API keys, DB URIs)
    .env         
    .env.*
    !.env.example
                
    # Python 
    __pycache__/
    *.py[cod]
    *.pyo
    .venv/     
    venv/
    *.egg-info/
                          
    # Frontend     
    frontend/node_modules/
    frontend/.next/
    frontend/out/
             
    # OS / editor
    .DS_Store
    *.swp   
    .idea/
    .vscode/   